$OpenBSD: patch-os-posix_c,v 1.1.2.1 2011/07/20 17:51:55 gsoares Exp $

Set groups properly for -runas.

-runas does not set supplementary group IDs.  This means that gid 0 (root)
is not dropped when switching to an unprivileged user.

CVE-2011-2527

--- os-posix.c.orig	Fri Oct 15 17:56:09 2010
+++ os-posix.c	Tue Jul 19 11:11:35 2011
